subject: Last CFP:: DINWC2015- Russia- IEEE
from: "The Third International Conference on Digital Information, Networking, and Wireless Communications (DINWC2015)" <donotreply@dcmrf.net>
body:
http://sdiwc.net/conferences/dinwc2015/

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
You are invited to participate in The Third International Conference on Digital Information, Networking, and Wireless Communications (DINWC2015) that will be held in Moscow, Russia on Feb. 3-5, 2015)

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
All the papers will be submitted to IEEE for potential inclusion to IEEE Xplore

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

Important dates

Submission Dates: Open from now until January 6, 2015
Notification of Acceptance: 3 weeks from the submission date
Camera Ready Submission: Open from now until January 21, 2015
Registration Deadline: Open from now until January 21, 2015
Conference Dates: February 3-5, 2015
